<br>
pps. Oh, and looking at it from a bard's perspective....bring it on.....my swarm kiting just became 5-10X more effective. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=omegasyphon>omegasyphon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 695<br> <font color=#333333>(1/16/03 3:56:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=449.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   comment</span><hr size=1> the easiest solution is to just change the exp rate a chanter gets using a charmed pet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pissed1vi2soe@themagicianstower>Pissed1VI2SOE</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 562<br> <font color=#333333>(1/16/03 3:57:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=449.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Charm solution? (Hopefully not redundant)</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> Theres mobs in POV, HOH, BOT, POS, etc etc which can all be DC'd and do more damage then your idea <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
